    <item>
      <title>巨额牛市交易结束，基金撤出铜市 200 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/funds-pull-20-billion-from-copper-as-mega-bull-trade-unravels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 5 月中旬以来，由于对中国需求的担忧加剧，基金经理已平仓了超过 200 亿美元的铜多头仓位，导致这种最重要的工业大宗商品之一的资金迅速流出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/funds-pull-20-billion-from-copper-as-mega-bull-trade-unravels</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 12:35:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于供应担忧缓解，阿拉比卡咖啡价格维持近三周低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/arabica-coffee-holds-near-three-week-low-on-easing-supply-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商评估了主要种植区巴西的天气条件好转以及运输速度加快有助于缓解供应紧张状况，阿拉比卡咖啡期货交易价格接近三周以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/arabica-coffee-holds-near-three-week-low-on-easing-supply-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 12:22:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
